reviewText: See it for the White Elvis Suit number alone.  A grand entrance. A fine dance. And for some reason, the costume changes mid-song and lights up like a christmas tree...only, the suit is so bulky from wires and lights, the actor looks 20 pounds heavier. But he dances in a lighted suit, so for my rupees, worth watching.  I rate it three curries out of a possible 5.
